text: (muhamedi hoyi!) beli፡- «yenigisina balebeti yehoniki alahi hoyi! lemitishawi sewi nigisinani tiset’alehi፡፡ kemitishawimi sewi nigisinani tigefifalehi፡፡ yemitishawinimi sewi talik’alehi፡፡ yemitishawinimi sewi tawaridalehi፡፡ melikami negeri hulu be’ijihi (bechilotahi) newi፤ anite benegeru hulu layi chayi nehina፡፡»
